      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n.tsukie-faq-pro{\n  background:#fdfbf7;\n  padding-bottom:0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-hero{\n  background:#f5f1ea;\n  padding:70px 40px 50px;\n  text-align:center;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-hero h1{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:60px;\n  font-weight:600;\n  font-style:italic;\n  margin:0 0 20px;\n  background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1e2a38 0%, #a08766 30%, #c9a77c 50%, #a08766 70%, #1e2a38 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip:text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;\n  background-clip:text;\n  line-height:1.1;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-divider{\n  display:flex;\n  align-items:center;\n  justify-content:center;\n  gap:14px;\n  max-width:320px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-line{\n  flex:1;\n  height:1px;\n  background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #a08766, transparent);\n}\n.tsukie-faq-body{\n  max-width:900px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n  padding:60px 40px 0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-item{\n  margin-bottom:40px;\n  padding-bottom:35px;\n  border-bottom:1px solid #e8e1d7;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-item:last-child{\n  border-bottom:none;\n  margin-bottom:0;\n  padding-bottom:0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-question{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:22px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#1e2a38;\n  margin:0 0 16px;\n  font-weight:600;\n  line-height:1.4;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-answer{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:15px;\n  line-height:1.8;\n  color:#4a4a4a;\n  margin:0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-answer ul{\n  margin:10px 0 0 0;\n  padding-left:20px;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-answer li{\n  margin-bottom:8px;\n  line-height:1.7;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-answer li:last-child{\n  margin-bottom:0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-answer strong{\n  color:#1e2a38;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-cta{\n  background:#1e2a38;\n  padding:50px 40px;\n  text-align:center;\n  margin:60px 0 0;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-cta h3{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:28px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#d4c5a9;\n  margin:0 0 12px;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-cta p{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:15px;\n  color:#d4c5a9;\n  margin:0 0 25px;\n  line-height:1.6;\n  max-width:700px;\n  margin-left:auto;\n  margin-right:auto;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-contact{\n  display:flex;\n  justify-content:center;\n  gap:25px;\n  flex-wrap:wrap;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-contact a{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:14px;\n  color:#a08766;\n  text-decoration:none;\n  font-weight:600;\n  letter-spacing:0.5px;\n  transition:color 0.3s ease;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-contact a:hover{\n  color:#c9a77c;\n}\n\n@media(max-width:749px){\n.tsukie-faq-hero{padding:50px 20px 40px}\n.tsukie-faq-hero h1{font-size:40px}\n.tsukie-faq-body{padding:45px 20px 0}\n.tsukie-faq-question{font-size:19px}\n.tsukie-faq-answer{font-size:14px}\n.tsukie-faq-item{margin-bottom:32px;padding-bottom:28px}\n.tsukie-faq-cta{\n  margin:45px 0 0;\n  padding:40px 25px;\n}\n.tsukie-faq-cta h3{font-size:24px}\n.tsukie-faq-contact{flex-direction:column;gap:15px}\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"tsukie-faq-pro\">\n  <div class=\"tsukie-faq-hero\">\n    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-divider\">\n      <span class=\"tsukie-faq-line\"></span>\n      <span style=\"color:#a08766;font-size:18px\">✦</span>\n      <span class=\"tsukie-faq-line\"></span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"tsukie-faq-body\">\n    \n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">1. How long do I have to request a return?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Within 7 days of delivery. Must be unused, with tags and original packaging intact.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">2. Which items cannot be returned? (If Any)</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Sale or clearance items</li>\n          <li>Customised/personalised products</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">3. What conditions must my product meet?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Unused, unwashed, unaltered</li>\n          <li>Tags, labels, and original packaging intact</li>\n          <li>Same condition as delivered</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">4. What if my item is damaged or wrong?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Contact us within 48 hours with clear photos.</li>\n          <li>We offer replacement or refund to original payment/store credit.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">5. Can I exchange for a different size or colour?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Yes! Direct exchanges are available if the item is in stock.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">6. How do I return a product?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Pickup arranged for most locations in India.</li>\n          <li>Self-ship if pickup is unavailable; reimbursement removed for now.</li>\n          <li>Process flow: Request → Pickup/Ship → Inspection (1-2 days) → Refund/Store Credit (3-5 days)</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">7. How are refunds processed?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Tsukie error: Refund to original payment method within 5-7 days, or store credit</li>\n          <li>Other valid returns: Store credit valid for 1 year</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">8. Can I cancel my order?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Before shipping:</strong> Full refund</li>\n          <li><strong>After shipping:</strong> Refuse delivery → store credit issued after inspection</li>\n          <li><strong>After delivery:</strong> Follow return process</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">9. Partial order returns?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>You may return some items; specify which, and we'll process accordingly</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">10. Late/missing deliveries?</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Contact us; we'll track, resolve delays, or initiate replacement/refund.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">11. Contact Tsukie for returns/questions:</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Email:</strong> connect@tsukie.in</li>\n          <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +91 9898778882</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"tsukie-faq-question\">12. Other notes:</h3>\n      <div class=\"tsukie-faq-answer\">\n        <ul>\n          <li>Handle items carefully and return in original packaging</li>\n          <li>Inspection within 1-2 days after receipt</li>\n          <li>Store credit valid 1 year</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"tsukie-faq-cta\">\n    <h3>Still have questions?</h3>\n    <p>Every piece you choose should make you happy, confident, and comfortable. If it doesn't, we'll work with you until it's right - no stress, no fuss, just the Tsukie care you deserve.</p>\n    <div class=\"tsukie-faq-contact\">\n      <a href=\"mailto:connect@tsukie.in\">connect@tsukie.in</a>\n      <a href=\"https://wa.me/919898778882\" target=\"_blank\">WhatsApp: +91 9898778882</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
