        "custom_liquid_L8kAjN": {
          "type": "custom-liquid",
          "name": "t:names.custom_liquid",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "{% if page.handle == 'about-us' %}\n<style>\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@1,400;1,600&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital@1&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');\n\n.tsukie-about-pro{\n  background:#fdfbf7;\n}\n.tsukie-about-hero-pro{\n  background:#f5f1ea;\n  padding:70px 40px 50px;\n  text-align:center;\n}\n.tsukie-about-hero-pro h1{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:60px;\n  font-weight:600;\n  font-style:italic;\n  margin:0 0 20px;\n  background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1e2a38 0%, #a08766 30%, #c9a77c 50%, #a08766 70%, #1e2a38 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip:text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;\n  background-clip:text;\n  line-height:1.1;\n}\n.tsukie-hero-divider{\n  display:flex;\n  align-items:center;\n  justify-content:center;\n  gap:14px;\n  max-width:320px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n}\n.tsukie-hero-line{\n  flex:1;\n  height:1px;\n  background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #a08766, transparent);\n}\n.tsukie-about-body{\n  max-width:900px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n  padding:70px 40px;\n}\n.tsukie-about-section{\n  margin-bottom:65px;\n}\n.tsukie-about-section:last-child{\n  margin-bottom:0;\n}\n.tsukie-about-section h2{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:38px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#1e2a38;\n  margin:0 0 24px;\n  font-weight:600;\n  position:relative;\n  padding-bottom:16px;\n}\n.tsukie-about-section h2:after{\n  content:'';\n  position:absolute;\n  bottom:0;\n  left:0;\n  width:60px;\n  height:2px;\n  background:linear-gradient(90deg, #a08766, #c9a77c);\n}\n.tsukie-about-section p{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:15px;\n  line-height:1.9;\n  color:#4a4a4a;\n  margin:0 0 18px;\n  font-weight:400;\n}\n.tsukie-about-section p strong{\n  color:#1e2a38;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n.tsukie-founder-block{\n  background:#f5f1ea;\n  padding:50px 40px;\n  border-left:3px solid #a08766;\n  margin:40px 0;\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:140px 1fr;\n  gap:30px;\n  align-items:center;\n}\n.tsukie-founder-img{\n  width:140px;\n  height:140px;\n  border-radius:50%;\n  object-fit:cover;\n  border:3px solid #d4c5a9;\n}\n.tsukie-founder-text p{\n  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;\n  font-size:20px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#1e2a38;\n  line-height:1.7;\n  margin:0 0 16px;\n}\n.tsukie-founder-name{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:14px;\n  letter-spacing:2px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  color:#a08766;\n  font-weight:600;\n  margin:0;\n}\n.tsukie-promise-box{\n  background:#1e2a38;\n  padding:60px 50px;\n  text-align:center;\n  margin:60px -40px -70px;\n}\n.tsukie-promise-box h2{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:36px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#d4c5a9;\n  margin:0 0 20px;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n.tsukie-promise-box h2:after{\n  display:none;\n}\n.tsukie-promise-box p{\n  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;\n  font-size:20px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#d4c5a9;\n  line-height:1.8;\n  margin:0 0 16px;\n}\n.tsukie-signature{\n  margin-top:40px;\n  padding-top:30px;\n  border-top:1px solid rgba(212,197,169,0.3);\n}\n.tsukie-signature-name{\n  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;\n  font-size:28px;\n  font-style:italic;\n  color:#d4c5a9;\n  margin:0 0 6px;\n}\n.tsukie-signature-title{\n  font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;\n  font-size:11px;\n  letter-spacing:2.5px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  color:#a08766;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n@media(max-width:749px){\n.tsukie-about-hero-pro{padding:50px 20px 40px}\n.tsukie-about-hero-pro h1{font-size:40px}\n.tsukie-about-body{padding:50px 20px}\n.tsukie-about-section h2{font-size:30px}\n.tsukie-about-section p{font-size:14px}\n.tsukie-founder-block{\n  grid-template-columns:1fr;\n  text-align:center;\n  padding:35px 25px;\n}\n.tsukie-founder-img{margin:0 auto}\n.tsukie-promise-box{\n  margin:50px -20px -50px;\n  padding:45px 25px;\n}\n.tsukie-promise-box h2{font-size:28px}\n.tsukie-promise-box p{font-size:18px}\n}\n</style>\n\n{% assign founder_image = page.content | split: '<img' | last | split: 'src=\"' | last | split: '\"' | first %}\n\n<div class=\"tsukie-about-pro\">\n  <div class=\"tsukie-about-hero-pro\">\n    <h1>About Tsukie</h1>\n    <div class=\"tsukie-hero-divider\">\n      <span class=\"tsukie-hero-line\"></span>\n      <span style=\"color:#a08766;font-size:18px\">✦</span>\n      <span class=\"tsukie-hero-line\"></span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"tsukie-about-body\">\n    <div class=\"tsukie-about-section\">\n      <p>For fifteen years, I worked in the corporate world, ten of those in e-commerce. I spent my days leading teams, solving problems, and working 12-14 hour shifts. I loved the work, but somewhere along the way, I started noticing something that stayed with me.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-about-section\">\n      <h2>The Observation</h2>\n      <p>I saw talented women, colleagues, friends, people I deeply respected, who had everything it took to rise. Yet somewhere between their capability and how the world saw them, there was a gap. It was subtle, but it was there. And over time, I started to wonder: what if the way we present ourselves could feel as effortless as the work we do? What if getting dressed wasn't another task to solve, but something that just... worked?</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"tsukie-founder-block\">\n        {% if founder_image contains 'cdn.shopify.com' %}\n          <img class=\"tsukie-founder-img\" src=\"{{ founder_image }}\" alt=\"Ankit Patawari\">\n        {% else %}\n          <img class=\"tsukie-founder-img\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1864/7741/2671/files/founder.jpg\" alt=\"Ankit Patawari\">\n        {% endif %}\n        <div class=\"tsukie-founder-text\">\n          <p>\"I'm Ankit Patawari, and that observation became Tsukie.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tsukie-founder-name\">Founder, Tsukie</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-about-section\">\n      <h2>The Leap</h2>\n      <p>When my team members and friends, the people who had seen me work, push, and deliver, started telling me I should do something of my own, it planted a seed. If I could give 12-14 hours to someone else's dream, why not to my own? Leaving my job as an Operations Manager, leading a team of 100 people, wasn't easy. The doubts were real: financial stability, the fear of failure, the comfort of a steady pay-check.</p>\n      <p>But it also felt like the end of one journey and the beginning of another. One where I could create something meaningful. One where I could, eventually, create opportunities for others too. Right now, it's just me, managing everything from design to delivery. But that's okay. Every big thing starts small.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-about-section\">\n      <h2>The Name</h2>\n      <p>The name <strong>Tsukie</strong> means \"moon\" in Japanese. But it also carries something deeply personal. In Hindi, the moon is called <strong>Chanda</strong>, my mother's name. She ran a small clothing business from home, selling clothes for children. Watching her work with such simplicity and grace taught me something important: that clothing isn't just fabric. It's care. It's confidence. It's connection.</p>\n      <p>She cheers me on now, from the sidelines, and her spirit is stitched into everything we do. Tsukie also echoes <strong>Sukhi</strong>, the Hindi word for happiness. And that's what I want every woman to feel when she wears our clothes. Happy. At ease. Confident.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tsukie-about-section\">\n      <h2>What We Create</h2>\n      <p>At Tsukie, we create semi-casual, semi-formal pieces that are designed to move with your life. One piece that works everywhere, from a morning meeting to an evening function, from the office to a weekend outing.</p>\n      <p>Because your day doesn't pause for outfit changes, and neither should your confidence.</p>\n      <p>We believe that when women feel good in what they're wearing, they show up differently. Not louder. Not trying harder. Just more <em>themselves</em>. And that quiet confidence? That's everything.</p>\n      <p>I've seen it. I've felt its absence. And now, I'm building something to fill that space.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"tsukie-promise-box\">\n    <h2>Our Promise</h2>\n    <p>Tsukie is grounded, simple, and elegant, just like the women it's made for. We're an Indian brand with roots we're proud of and a vision that reaches beyond borders.</p>\n    <p>Our values: happiness, quality, affordability, and inclusiveness, aren't just words. They're promises.</p>\n    <p>This journey is still unfolding, and I'm learning every day. But one thing I know for sure: fashion should make you feel like you belong, in the room, in your skin, in your story.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"tsukie-promise-box\" style=\"background:transparent;padding:0;margin:50px 0 0;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:#d4c5a9;margin-bottom:16px;\">Join Us</h2>\n      <p>This is Tsukie. And I'd love for you to be part of it.</p>\n      <p>Because here, you don't just wear clothes.<br>You wear a feeling.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"tsukie-signature\">\n        <p class=\"tsukie-signature-name\">Ankit Patawari</p>\n        <p class=\"tsukie-signature-title\">Founder, Tsukie</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n{% else %}\n<div class=\"page-width\" style=\"padding:40px 20px;\">\n  <h1 style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">{{ page.title }}</h1>\n  <div class=\"rte\">\n    {{ page.content }}\n  </div>\n</div>\n{% endif %}"
